Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: libprague (= ${Source-Version}), libwarsaw (= ${Source-Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Core library for the Berlin display server
 This is the serverside implementation of Berlin's CORBA interfaces.

