Package: warsaw-idl
Section: devel
Architecture: all
Depends: omniorb
Description: Communication library for the Berlin display server (CORBA IDL)
 These IDL-files define the Berlin display server's interfaces. They are
 its equivalent to the X-protocol.

Package: berlin-kit-command
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: libberlin (= ${Source-Version}), libprague (= ${Source-Version}), libwarsaw (= ${Source-Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: CommandKit for the Berlin display server
 The CommandKit implements simple models that are observed by the more
 complex Kits. As all Kits it gets loaded into the server at runtime.
 .
 All Berlin clients need this Kit.

